chimera-nfsv3: fix shutdown

The NFSv3 server contains a shutdown method 'destroy', however this 
method isn't called from Spring, so the NFS server isn't shut down 
cleanly.

This patch adds the call to destroy to cleanly shutdown the server.

Target: trunk
Patch: http://rb.dcache.org/r/2994/
